invalid type: string "When can I terminate my plan?\nOn the anniversary date of the plan in accordance with the French\nlaw on infra-annual termination, with no supporting document to be\nprovided.\nTermination will be effective in accordance with the general terms and\nconditions of the plan within a minimum of one month of receipt of your\ndo so, view the list of in-network\nns\n;t’’’’’’’’’’’’’